      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with plenty of potential. This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a low-cost entry point, a project, or basic around-town utility. Priced to reflect its condition while still delivering solid value for the right owner.",
      "price": 4900.0,
