    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t pretending to be perfect, but it\u2019s an affordable option for someone handy, a first-time fixer, or anyone who just needs something budget-friendly with plenty of potential. It\u2019s being sold honestly as-is, and for the right buyer it could be a great way into motoring without spending a fortune. Come have a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with solid enthusiast potential. Runs and moves, with an engine that pulls cleanly through the rev range and a drivetrain that feels fundamentally intact. Shows its age cosmetically and will benefit from reconditioning, but the core package is there for someone wanting an affordable entry point, weekend wrenching candidate, or budget build. Straightforward, mechanical feel, honest wear, and plenty of upside for the next owner.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Used and rough, but ready to go. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is the kind of car that still has a story left to tell. Honest, well-traveled, and full of everyday grit, it offers a chance to get behind the wheel without stretching the budget. Perfect for someone who appreciates a machine with character, whether you need a practical around-town driver, a backup vehicle, or a project to make your own. It\u2019s not pretending to be showroom fresh\u2014that\u2019s exactly the charm. What it does offer is presence, purpose, and the kind of value that\u2019s getting harder to find.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
