      "description": "Affordable and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical option for a value-focused buyer seeking dependable transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who appreciates a straightforward, budget-conscious purchase with plenty of potential. A sensible opportunity to get behind the wheel without stretching your budget.",
      "price": 5495.0,
